     <i>IndexStart</i> for this purpose:<br>
     <i>WriteNumberedList('Hobbies (3)',tempStringList,'Hobby_',0);</i>
     procudes:<br>
     [Hobbies (3)]<br>
     Count=3<br>
     Hobby_0=Computing<br>
     Hobby_1=Music<br>
     Hobby_2=Shopping<br>
     <br>
